{"type":"message","id":"17780b7b","parentId":"7e3ac771","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:10:10.765Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t5d3o4vg6iut_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"cheaper alternatives to U-Haul moving truck rental 2026\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 940,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ab073dbda5ef263f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n5 Best U-Haul Alternatives & Competitors (2026 Guide)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ab073dbda5ef263f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.movebuddha.com/blog/u-haul-competitors/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cb493cc0bbb6d1e3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPenske often includes unlimited mileage on one-ways, which can simplify budgeting for cross-country drives. Need the cheapest deal: <strong>Budget Truck Rental</strong> frequently posts the lowest base rates and strong discounts for students, military, and AARP ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cb493cc0bbb6d1e3\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"3 weeks ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.movebuddha.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3b617bdce795d980\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCheapest Truck Rental Companies (2026): Budget vs U-Haul vs Penske | Move.org\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3b617bdce795d980\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.move.org/best-cheap-truck-rental-companies/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"71807e44d7a6e83e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Budget Truck Rental</strong> is usually the cheaper option for local moves and smaller homes. The company frequently offers lower base rates than U-Haul, and its long list of discounts — like those for students, military members, and AARP customers ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"71807e44d7a6e83e\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 16, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.move.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9321366007ab1c6d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n5 Best Moving Truck Rental Companies of 2026 | Move.org\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9321366007ab1c6d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.move.org/best-moving-truck-rental-companies/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"de88513a6065b8cb\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nBudget is still hard to beat for low local prices, The <strong>Home Depot</strong> is great for quick DIY moves, U-Haul wins on availability, and Enterprise offers one of the widest selections of truck sizes.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"de88513a6065b8cb\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 10, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.move.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"56ca959083c4ef3f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nBest U-Haul Alternatives in 2026: Competitor Prices, Reviews and More - Moving Advice from HireAHelper\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"56ca959083c4ef3f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.hireahelper.com/top-uhaul-alternatives/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b5bdd5ba2e5cecd0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nBecause it reflects the full cost of a truck rental, it gives us a clearer way to compare each alternative to U-Haul and see which options provide better value. Looking at the truck rental comparison for a short local move, <strong>Budget Truck Rental</strong> is ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b5bdd5ba2e5cecd0\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 24, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.hireahelper.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fffb5d25c1deaf5e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCheaper Alternatives to U-Haul in 2026 (Compared)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fffb5d25c1deaf5e\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://citizenshipper.com/blog/cheaper-alternative-to-uhaul/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3aea8be5de7810f1\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nU-Haul has competitors such as <strong>Penske or Budget</strong>, but their prices are roughly the same. Choosing who to rent a truck from, you’re more likely to be guided by convenience than cost.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3aea8be5de7810f1\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 24, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"citizenshipper.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"cheaper alternatives to U-Haul moving truck rental 2026","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":940,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ab073dbda5ef263f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n5 Best U-Haul Alternatives & Competitors (2026 Guide)\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ab073dbda5ef263f\">>>","url":"https://www.movebuddha.com/blog/u-haul-competitors/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cb493cc0bbb6d1e3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPenske often includes unlimited mileage on one-ways, which can simplify budgeting for cross-country drives. Need the cheapest deal: <strong>Budget Truck Rental</strong> frequently posts the lowest base rates and strong discounts for students, military, and AARP ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cb493cc0bbb6d1e3\">>>","published":"3 weeks ago","siteName":"www.movebuddha.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3b617bdce795d980\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCheapest Truck Rental Companies (2026): Budget vs U-Haul vs Penske | Move.org\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNT