{"type":"message","id":"22638adf","parentId":"43836e80","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:26:40.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to add a section with the $13,000 loan from his mom. He asks if he'd have $13,969 with the $13,000 added.\n\nCurrent theoretical total after U-Haul and before rent: $4,669\nWith mom's loan: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669\n\nWait, let me re-read. After U-Haul ($700) and earning goal ($4,000) and starting cash ($1,369), Bobby has $4,669.\n\nWith mom's loan of $13,000: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669\n\nAfter 1st month rent ($1,850): $17,669 - $1,850 = $15,819\n\n\nAfter 2nd month rent ($1,850): $15,819 - $1,850 = $13,969\n\nSo yes, after two months he'd have $13,969 left, which matches what Bobby calculated.","thinkingSignature":"a3450ede8fa22973fdbfda3dda483fdfb5c30f72b870c3db93eea53eafb26cf9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l2zeznjd3ban_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> ~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md << 'EOF'\n\n## WITH Mom's Loan ($13,000)\n- Starting cash + earnings + U-Haul: $4,669\n- Plus mom's loan: +$13,000\n- **Total with loan (pre-rent): $17,669**\n\n- After 1st month rent: $17,669 - $1,850 = **$15,819**\n- After 2nd month rent: $15,819 - $1,850 = **$13,969**\n\n## Mom's Loan Repayment Terms\n- Loan amount: $13,000\n- Minimum payment: $411/month\n- Can pay earlier at any time\n\nEOF\necho \"Done\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":172,"output":382,"cacheRead":61187,"cacheWrite":525,"totalTokens":62266,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777418777022,"responseId":"0640751948205699eb83aab8ab6cbfe3"}}
