{"type":"message","id":"9d60a3ff","parentId":"bbedf6f4","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:26:49.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me confirm: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669. After 2 months rent ($1,850 × 2 = $3,700), $17,669 - $3,700 = $13,969. Yes that's correct.","thinkingSignature":"119c46a3904493702c0c321017ddb7d3d3a609f88e242b6f9f47f13f87c84f85"},{"type":"text","text":"Yeah you got it — **$13,969** after 2 months rent with mom's loan included. The $13k makes a big difference. At $411/month minimum it takes about 32 months to pay off ($13,000 ÷ $411 ≈ 31.6 months)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30348,"output":118,"cacheRead":31935,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62401,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777418804986,"responseId":"064075357e6f110da411d7b25a630a07"}}
