{"type":"message","id":"a87e9df4","parentId":"82f7ad0f","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:43:43.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see that Rex uses its own Telegram bot account (`telegram:g-agent-rex-telegram-direct-8212808444`). When Rex sends messages, they come from the Rex Telegram bot, not from me (Dean). \n\nBobby said \"rex is telling me that he cant get in contact with you\" - meaning Rex was trying to send messages to Dean but they weren't going through. \n\nThis is likely because Rex tried to message me through some mechanism but I'm the main session and don't receive messages from sub-agents in that way. The issue is architectural - agents trying to communicate with each other through Telegram doesn't work because they're separate bot accounts.\n \nSo the real problem is that Rex's Telegram bot is only authorized to talk to Bobby, not to other agents. When Rex tries to reach out to Dean, the message fails because there's no established communication channel between them - they're isolated on separate bot accounts. I should be direct with Bobby about this architectural limitation and suggest a proper way for agents to coordinate if that's needed.","thinkingSignature":"349dcf45236fe26f58acd2ad40dc49602bd2c33c5cfdb1dced42b4612867282b"},{"type":"text","text":"Found the issue. Rex is running on his own Telegram bot account (`@g_agent_rex_bot`). When he tries to message me, it goes to his own Telegram DM with Bobby — not to me.\n\nWe're not actually connected as agents. The way Bobby has it set up, Rex works independently and sends results to you on Telegram. Rex can't reach me directly because we're separate agents on separate bot accounts.\n\nIf you want Rex and I to be able to communicate, I need to know how you want that to work — or it might not be set up that way at all. What's the goal here? Were you expecting Rex to report findings to me automatically?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51874,"output":343,"cacheRead":31935,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84152,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777423410194,"responseId":"064087323f2494c4cdbe8d9f43927527"}}
